WEBVTT

00:02.757 --> 00:04.437
Feel free to scurry to him again.

00:04.790 --> 00:06.548
I can fight my own battles.

00:06.550 --> 00:09.748
What you've achieved in one day
is nothing short of miraculous.

00:09.750 --> 00:12.228
It augurs well
for how you'll manage with George.

00:12.230 --> 00:15.228
We wouldn't want him
suspecting collusion.

00:15.230 --> 00:18.428
Just so you know,
I've never told anyone about us.

00:18.430 --> 00:19.990
Step away from the car.

00:24.830 --> 00:26.308
No, I love you.

00:26.310 --> 00:28.188
I love you, Sarah.

00:28.190 --> 00:30.868
But you will help me, won't you?

00:30.870 --> 00:34.588
If you are pregnant, perhaps.
It's very complicated.

00:34.590 --> 00:37.230
What am I going to do?

